  <description>
    This module contains a fork of the javaparser project,
    which uses javacc to generate a java language parser.

    http://github.com/javaparser/javaparser -> git@github.com:WeTheInternet/javaparser.git

    The fork adds support for `template string,
    which do not require escaping any characters,
    except the \` tick character, for nice, easy
    to write multi-line strings`.

    This fork also includes support for expression
    structures that resemble html, json and css.
    See README for details.
  </description>


